{"tid":339863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高鐵一地兩檢正仆街","createTime":"2017-07-29T12:00:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T05:22:53.000Z","uid":96231,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5689ba016de89f43670cf35bb1cb7b7d4a7d4cc6","tid":339863,"uid":96231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:00:51.000Z","msg":"［純討論］點解係要用全面法律呢？<br />\n建議：點解唔將大陸出境同入境部份改做大使館？<br />\n求法律JJ解答可行性<br />\n<br />\n出境程序：離境香港後，進入內地領使館，完成檢查後，獲發允許入境簽證，代替入境手續，離開領館進入月台後，依舊實施香港法律，但已辦理離境手續，類似機場嘅離境大堂，直至內地邊境界後，便直接憑簽證自動入境。<br />\n<br />\n入境程序：由內地進入香港，進入香港邊境時自動實行香港法律，進入西九龍站入境層後，領事館將可行使外交特權，將未獲淮進入香港的人，原車遣返。但若該等人士一直留於月台區，將不作理會。<br />\n<br />\n有咁多方案揀，仲要理由全面性實行全國法律做一地兩檢。"},{"pid":"11f16809a0b900f3b64d4a12c2a0558ab7f5b8de","tid":339863,"uid":96231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:22:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"357f36be47ae21263f088897983160ac0aedf484","tid":339863,"uid":96231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:22:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8678032601482353ce65c7da2c1bf4c8f648999","tid":339863,"uid":96231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:22:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86da6fd99bb46abf817da5947ca6388c693dc6a8","tid":339863,"uid":96231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T02:38:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84d8e67b688697d23985a13937a56b5f858221fb","tid":339863,"uid":96231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:03:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83adc4c36c5321c9d69be22d576b2067c2534d95","tid":339863,"uid":96231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:03:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cab1116156f13586ba6b54a5eb50ecd91388140c","tid":339863,"uid":96231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:03:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58812135959be45b344e33790d76923e1678f376","tid":339863,"uid":96231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07